data.description: location! location! location.  This is where you want to live in the sought after Villages of Barrington Downs in Gainsway Village at the corner of Kentucky Derby and Sweepstakes.  This family homes has fond and forever memories. This two story beauty has 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. The house has an open floor plan.  The family room host a wood burning fireplace, bay window and sliding  patio doors leading to the concrete patio and large fenced backyard.  The house  has new furnace, new hot water heater, newer wood floors, updated decorative  light fixtures, stainless steel appliances and ac services and recharged in 2023.  The basement is ready for your  completion, personalization and style. Home warranty plan being  offered  along with $2000 for cosmetic updates. The house is in move in condition.   Needs TLC. Home is being sold As Is -seller will do no repairs nor pay for inspections including municipal. Seller may pay some closing cost.  Possibly no money down and point buy down.
